# Development Workflow

## Runtime Validation
```bash
pnpm run dev
# Backend: http://localhost:5000
# Frontend: https://localhost:5173/
# Health: http://localhost:5000/api/health/ping
# Swagger: http://localhost:5000/swagger
```

## Build Commands
```bash
# Build everything
pnpm build

# Build backend only
pnpm build:backend

# Build frontend only
pnpm build:frontend
```

## Testing Commands
```bash
# Run all tests
pnpm test

# Run backend tests
cd backend && dotnet test

# Run frontend tests
cd frontend && pnpm test
```

## Database Operations
```bash
# Initialize database
sqlcmd -S "(localdb)\mssqllocaldb" -i "backend\Ikhtibar.Infrastructure\Data\InitializeDatabase.sql"

# Seed database
sqlcmd -S "(localdb)\mssqllocaldb" -i "backend\seed-app-db.sql"
```

## File Structure Reference

### Backend:
```
backend/
├── Ikhtibar.API/Controllers/     # API endpoints
├── Ikhtibar.Core/Entities/       # Domain entities
├── Ikhtibar.Core/Repositories/   # Repository interfaces
├── Ikhtibar.Core/Services/       # Service interfaces
└── Ikhtibar.Infrastructure/      # Implementations
```

### Frontend:
```
frontend/src/
├── modules/[feature]/            # Feature modules
├── shared/components/            # Reusable components
├── shared/services/              # API services
├── shared/store/                 # Global state
└── shared/types/                 # TypeScript types
```
